  "text": "The majority of snuff users in the current were between 35-54 years old. This finding is in agreement with Wray and Guirt study [CITATION_1] that reported the middle-aged are the biggest group of snuff users. The findings of this study showed that there was no significant difference between various age groups with respect to oral lesion involvement. These results are in contrast to the findings of Reichart and Mohr [CITATION_2] and Wray and Guirt studies [CITATION_3] . This might be due to the wide range of age of participants in our study.",
